<!-- *****************************  rsv attributes      **************************************** -->
<section id="customizing-rsv-attrs-osg" xreflabel="Customizing OSG rsv attrs">
<title>Customizing RSV attrs</title>

<para>
Attributes used to configure rsv.
</para>

<para>

<table frame='all'><title>Attributes Used in OSG Roll RSV Customization</title>
<tgroup cols='2' align='left' colsep='1' rowsep='1'>
<thead>
<row>
  <entry align="center">Attibute Name</entry>
  <entry align="center">Description</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>

<row>
<entry>
OSG_rsvuid
</entry>
<entry>
Configure uid value for rsv user. Default: 5452
</entry>
</row>

<row>
<entry>
OSG_rsvgid
</entry>
<entry>
Configure gid value for rsv group. Default: 5452
</entry>
</row>

<row>
<entry>
OSG_cndrcronuid
</entry>
<entry>
Configure uid value for condor cron user "cndrcron". Default: 466
</entry>
</row>

<row>
<entry>
OSG_cndrcrongid
</entry>
<entry>
Configure gid value for condor cron group "cndrcron". Default: 467
</entry>
</row>

<row>
<entry>
OSG_RSV_Port
</entry>
<entry>
Configure RSV Web port. Default: 80
</entry>
</row>

<row>
<entry>
OSG_RSV_SPort
</entry>
<entry>
Configure RSV Secure Web port. Default: 443
</entry>
</row>

<row>
<entry>
OSG_RSVGFTPList
</entry>
<entry>
Configure in RSV list of gridftp servers (comma separated). No default. If not defined, try content of rocks attr OSG_GFTPServer. 
</entry>
</row>

<row>
<entry>
OSG_RSVSRMTestDir
</entry>
<entry>
Configure RSV srm_dir in case there is a SRM Server to probe. This should be the directory used to probe. No default.
</entry>
</row>



</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>

</para>

</section>

